<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>NearMates User Guide</title>
    <style>
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }

        body {
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #333;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%);
            min-height: 100vh;
            padding: 20px;
        }

        .container {
            max-width: 900px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            background: white;
            border-radius: 15px;
            box-shadow: 0 20px 60px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
            overflow: hidden;
        }

        .header {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%);
            color: white;
            padding: 40px 30px;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .header h1 {
            font-size: 2.5em;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            font-weight: 700;
        }

        .header p {
            font-size: 1.1em;
            opacity: 0.95;
        }

        .back-button {
            display: inline-flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 8px;
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2);
            color: white;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            border: 2px solid white;
            border-radius: 25px;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-weight: 600;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        .back-button:hover {
            background: white;
            color: #667eea;
            transform: translateX(-5px);
        }

        .content {
            padding: 40px 30px;
        }

        .intro {
            background: #f8f9ff;
            padding: 20px;
            border-left: 4px solid #667eea;
            border-radius: 8px;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }

        .step {
            margin-bottom: 35px;
            padding-bottom: 35px;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #e0e0e0;
        }

        .step:last-child {
            border-bottom: none;
        }

        .step-number {
            display: inline-block;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%);
            color: white;
            width: 40px;
            height: 40px;
            border-radius: 50%;
            text-align: center;
            line-height: 40px;
            font-weight: bold;
            margin-right: 15px;
            font-size: 1.2em;
        }

        .step h2 {
            display: inline-block;
            color: #667eea;
            font-size: 1.6em;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            vertical-align: middle;
        }

        .step p {
            margin: 15px 0;
            font-size: 1.05em;
            color: #555;
        }

        .step ol, .step ul {
            margin: 15px 0 15px 40px;
        }

        .step li {
            margin: 10px 0;
            font-size: 1.05em;
            color: #555;
        }

        .tip-box {
            background: #fff9e6;
            border-left: 4px solid #ffc107;
            padding: 15px;
            margin: 15px 0;
            border-radius: 5px;
        }

        .tip-box strong {
            color: #f57c00;
        }

        .button-group {
            display: flex;
            gap: 15px;
            padding: 15px;
            background: #f5f5f5;
            border-radius: 8px;
            margin-top: 10px;
        }

        .action-button {
            flex: 1;
            padding: 12px 20px;
            border: none;
            border-radius: 6px;
            font-weight: 600;
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
            text-decoration: none;
            text-align: center;
            display: block;
        }

        .primary-btn {
            background: #667eea;
            color: white;
        }

        .primary-btn:hover {
            background: #5568d3;
            transform: translateY(-2px);
            box-shadow: 0 5px 15px rgba(102, 126, 234, 0.3);
        }

        .secondary-btn {
            background: white;
            color: #667eea;
            border: 2px solid #667eea;
        }

        .secondary-btn:hover {
            background: #667eea;
            color: white;
        }

        .footer {
            background: #f8f9fa;
            padding: 30px;
            text-align: center;
            color: #666;
        }

        .footer h3 {
            color: #667eea;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }

        .highlight {
            background: #e8eaf6;
            padding: 2px 6px;
            border-radius: 3px;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #667eea;
        }

        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            .header h1 {
                font-size: 2em;
            }

            .content {
                padding: 30px 20px;
            }

            .step h2 {
                font-size: 1.3em;
                display: block;
                margin-top: 10px;
            }

            .button-group {
                flex-direction: column;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
           
            <h1>üåê NearMates User Guide</h1>
            <p>Your Complete Guide to Connecting with Your Community</p>
        </div>

        <div class="content">
            <div class="intro">
                <p><strong>Welcome to NearMates</strong> ‚Äì your platform for connecting with like-minded individuals nearby. Follow these steps to get started and make the most of your experience.</p>
            </div>

         

            <div class="step">
                <span class="step-number">1</span>
                <h2>Account Registration</h2>
                <p>If you are a new user:</p>
                <ol>
                    <li>Click on the <span class="highlight">Sign Up</span> or <span class="highlight">Create Account</span> button</li>
                    <li>Complete the registration form with the following information:
                        <ul>
                            <li>Full name</li>
                            <li>Email address</li>
                            <li>Secure password</li>
                            <li>Additional required details</li>
                        </ul>
                    </li>
                    <li>Click <span class="highlight">Register</span> to create your account</li>
                    <li>You will be automatically redirected to the login page</li>
                </ol>
            </div>

            <div class="step">
                <span class="step-number">2</span>
                <h2>User Authentication</h2>
                <p>To access your account:</p>
                <ol>
                    <li>Enter your registered email address</li>
                    <li>Provide your password</li>
                    <li>Click <span class="highlight">Login</span></li>
                    <li>You will be directed to your personalized dashboard</li>
                </ol>
            </div>

            <div class="step">
                <span class="step-number">3</span>
                <h2>Dashboard Overview</h2>
                <p>After successful login, you will see the main navigation interface with access to:</p>
                <ul>
                    <li><strong>Home</strong> ‚Äì Your main dashboard</li>
                    <li><strong>Profile</strong> ‚Äì Your personal information and settings</li>
                    <li><strong>Nearby Users</strong> ‚Äì Discover people in your vicinity</li>
                    <li><strong>Notifications</strong> ‚Äì Friend requests and updates</li>
                </ul>
                <div class="tip-box">
                    <strong>üí° Pro Tip:</strong> Begin by creating your profile to unlock the full potential of NearMates and start connecting with others.
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="step">
                <span class="step-number">4</span>
                <h2>Profile Creation and Customization</h2>
                <p><strong>Important First Step:</strong> Complete your profile before exploring the platform.</p>
                <ol>
                    <li>Navigate to <span class="highlight">Profile</span> from the main menu</li>
                    <li>Upload a profile picture</li>
                    <li>Add or update your information:
                        <ul>
                            <li>Username</li>
                            <li>Bio/Introduction</li>
                            <li>Interests and hobbies</li>
                            <li>Location preferences</li>
                        </ul>
                    </li>
                    <li>Click <span class="highlight">Save</span> or <span class="highlight">Update Profile</span></li>
                </ol>
                <p>Your profile is now visible to other users on the platform.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="step">
                <span class="step-number">5</span>
                <h2>Discovering Connections</h2>
                <p>To find and connect with other users:</p>
                <ol>
                    <li>Visit the <span class="highlight">Explore</span>, <span class="highlight">Nearby Users</span>, or <span class="highlight">Similar Interests</span> section</li>
                    <li>Browse through user profile cards displaying:
                        <ul>
                            <li>Profile pictures</li>
                            <li>Basic information</li>
                            <li>Shared interests</li>
                        </ul>
                    </li>
                    <li>Interact with profiles using available options:
                        <ul>
                            <li><strong>View Profile</strong> ‚Äì See detailed information</li>
                            <li><strong>Send Request</strong> ‚Äì Initiate a connection</li>
                            <li><strong>Message</strong> ‚Äì Start a conversation (if available)</li>
                        </ul>
                    </li>
                </ol>
            </div>

            <div class="step">
                <span class="step-number">6</span>
                <h2>Managing Connection Requests</h2>
                <p>To handle incoming friend requests:</p>
                <ol>
                    <li>Click the <span class="highlight">Notifications</span> icon in the navigation bar</li>
                    <li>Review all pending friend requests</li>
                    <li>Choose to <span class="highlight">Accept</span> or <span class="highlight">Decline</span> each request</li>
                    <li>A green indicator badge appears when you have new notifications</li>
                </ol>
            </div>

            <div class="step">
                <span class="step-number">7</span>
                <h2>Communication Features</h2>
                <p>Once connections are established:</p>
                <ul>
                    <li>Access your friends list</li>
                    <li>Initiate conversations through the messaging feature</li>
                    <li>View enhanced profile information of your connections</li>
                    <li>Interact based on the features available in your version</li>
                </ul>
            </div>

            <div class="step">
                <span class="step-number">8</span>
                <h2>Account Security</h2>
                <p>When you finish your session:</p>
                <ol>
                    <li>Locate the <span class="highlight">Logout</span> option in the navigation menu or user dropdown</li>
                    <li>Click <span class="highlight">Logout</span></li>
                    <li>You will be securely signed out and redirected to the login page</li>
                </ol>
            </div>

            <div class="button-group">
                <a href="javascript:history.back()" class="action-button secondary-btn">‚Üê Go Back</a>
                <a href="/Dashboard" class="action-button primary-btn">Home </a>
                <a href="/profile" class="action-button secondary-btn">Profile</a>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="footer">
            <h3>Need Assistance?</h3>
            <p>If you encounter any issues or have questions about using NearMates,<br>please contact our support team or refer to the FAQ section.</p>
            <p style="margin-top: 20px; font-style: italic; color: #667eea;"><strong>NearMates</strong> ‚Äì Connecting You with Your Community</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>